                    name = "Ollama",
                    available = true,
                )
            ),
        )

        val afterError = state.withRuntimeError(
            envelope(
                type = MessageType.Error,
                requestId = "hello-request",
                serializer = ErrorPayload.serializer(),
                payload = ErrorPayload(
                    code = "authentication_required",
                    message = "Pair this device first",
                    retryable = false,
                ),
